= Extracted Lists
<extracted-lists>
The list environments below are extracted from arXiv LaTeX source and
wrapped for pdfLaTeX validation.

+ For each ramification index, there are two possible values for
  #mi(`\alpha_1`).

+ When #mi(`\alpha_1 = -1`), although the DS operator has apparent
  singularity at #mi(`z=0`), corresponding solution is perfectly
  regular.

+ When #mi(`\alpha_1=-1/2`), the monodromy matrix is not diagonalizable,
  and this case is not covered by the present analysis. This is the
  so-called parabolic case.
